Miscellaneous Highlights: The Subway Socceroos come up against China PR in their third FIFA World Cup 2026 round three qualifying match on Thursday 10 October at Adelaide Oval.
Others: Tickets for the match start from $15 Child, $20 Concession, $29 Adult, and $58 Family.
The Socceroos have enjoyed plenty of success at Adelaide Oval in the past, including a 3-0 win vs New Zealand in 2011, a 7-0 win vs Tajikistan in 2016, and a 3-2 win vs Saudi Arabia in 2017.
